Purpose:
Make sure the on screen keyboard can be dismissed and re-enabled when the input field is re-selected

Steps:
1. Run notepad app
2. Tap on a note to start editing. The OSK will appear
3. Swipe down on the OSK to dismiss it
4. Tap on the input field again

Verification:
1. The on screen keyboard must appear after selecting the input field after it has been dismissed.